Source: re2
Priority: extra
Maintainer: PFI & NTT <jubatus@googlegroups.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.0.0), autotools-dev, perl
Standards-Version: 3.9.3
Section: libs
Homepage: http://re2.googlecode.com/

Package: libre2-0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: efficient, principled regular expression library
 RE2 is a fast, safe, thread-friendly alternative to 
 backtracking regular expression engines like those used 
 in PCRE, Perl, and Python. It is a C++ library.

Package: libre2-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libre2-0 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Headers and libraries for re2
 This package provides headers and libraries needed to
 develop applications using re2.
